nodes.text: During the Imperial Era, an individual served as a commander in the Galactic Empire and was deployed to the planet Zeffo. When the Jedi Cal Kestis undertook a mission to Zeffo, the commander was killed and one of their subordinates, a scout trooper, was reassigned to Kashyyyk along with Purge Troopers of the Inquisitorius. Eventually, Kestis returned to Kashyyyk and confronted the scout trooper as well as the other Imperial forces.
